public interface JanusGraphVertexProperty<V>
extends JanusGraphRelation, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.VertexProperty<V>, JanusGraphProperty<V>
JanusGraphProperty is a JanusGraphRelation connecting a vertex to a value. JanusGraphProperty extends JanusGraphRelation, with methods for retrieving the property's value and key.

Matthias Bröcheler (me@matthiasb.com);
